  "reverse": {
    "description": "Crowned ornate high shield with arms of Denmark, Norway and Kalmar Union, is bent to right. The shield has a big grass and a Royal Orb on the left; while at right is a trident, a banner of the Danish West Indies Company, a caduceus and some gold coins. Mintmark is in exergue",
    "lettering": "PRUDENTIA ET CONSTANTIA.\r\n______\r\nV.H.",
